headline: Welltower: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: The Toledo, Ohio-based real estate investment trust said it had funds from operations of $715.9 million, or $1.13 per share, in the period. The average estimate of seven analysts surveyed by Zacks Investment Research was for funds from operations of $1.12 per share. Funds from operations is a closely watched measure in the REIT industry.
